column3: SELECT * FROM testerdetails INNER JOIN testresult ON testerdetails.testid = testresult.testerid INNER JOIN testanswer ON testanswer.testerid = testerdetails.testid INNER JOIN upload ON testanswer.category = upload.category AND testanswer.question = upload.question AND testanswer.testname = upload.testname AND testanswer.qnid = 'OAT823' AND testanswer.category = 'Software Skill Test' AND testanswer.testname = 'Javascript'ORDER BY testanswer.id ASC
INNER JOIN testresult ON testerdetails.testid = testresult.testerid
